title: 3rd Annual Venice Beach Stouts N Staches Fest
desc: Local businesses come together to raise money for the   Foundation Taking over Venice Beach, Mo Bros and Mo Sistas will flood the streets in their MOs and moustache gear and have a fan-stache-tic time for a good cause.
